<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="my">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Character Chat Bot SPA</title>
<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
<style>
    .no-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
    .no-scrollbar { -ms-overflow-style: none; scrollbar-width: none; }
    #chatLog::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; }
    #chatLog::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background-color: #cbd5e1; border-radius: 10px; }
    
    /* Hover effect for edit button */
    .msg-bubble:hover .edit-btn { display: flex; }
</style>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-800 font-sans antialiased min-h-screen flex flex-col">

<header class="bg-white border-b border-slate-200 sticky top-0 z-20 shadow-sm">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center justify-between gap-3">
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 tracking-tight flex items-center gap-2">
            🎭 <span class="bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-purple-600">ဇာတ်ကောင်စကားပြောခန်း (Unrestricted)</span>
        </h1>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span id="syncStatus" class="text-xs font-medium text-indigo-600 bg-indigo-50 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md border border-indigo-100 flex items-center gap-1">
                ☁️ ချိတ်ဆက်နေသည်...
            </span>
            <div class="text-sm text-slate-500 bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full hidden sm:block border border-slate-200">Gemini 2.5 Pro</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</header>

<main class="flex-grow flex flex-col lg:flex-row max-w-7xl mx-auto w-full p-4 gap-6 h-[calc(100vh-76px)]">

    <div id="leftSidebar" class="w-full lg:w-1/3 flex flex-col gap-4 overflow-y-auto pr-2 pb-4 transition-all duration-300">
        
        <section class="bg-white p-5 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
            <details class="group">
                <summary class="text-md font-bold flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer list-none">
                    <span class="flex items-center gap-2">👤 ကျွန်ုပ်၏ ကိုယ်ရေးအချက်အလက်</span>
                    <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
                        <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="mt-4 flex flex-col gap-2">
                    <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">ဇာတ်ကောင်များမှ သင့်အကြောင်းကို သိရှိနားလည်စေရန် ထည့်သွင်းပါ။</p>
                    <textarea id="userPersonaInput" class="w-full min-h-[100px] p-3 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all resize-none text-sm" placeholder="ဥပမာ - ကျွန်တော့်နာမည်က... အသက်က... ဝါသနာက..."></textarea>
                    <div class="flex justify-end">
                        <span id="userPersonaSavedStatus" class="text-xs text-green-600 hidden items-center gap-1">✓ သိမ်းဆည်းပြီးပါပြီ</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </details>
        </section>

        <section class="bg-white p-5 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-3">
                <h2 class="text-md font-bold flex items-center gap-2">👥 ဇာတ်ကောင်များ</h2>
                <button id="createNewCharBtn" class="text-xs bg-indigo-600 text-white px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-indigo-700 font-medium transition-colors">
                    + အသစ်
                </button>
            </div>
            <div id="characterList" class="flex flex-col gap-2 max-h-40 overflow-y-auto pr-1">
                <div class="text-xs text-slate-400 italic py-2 text-center">ဇာတ်ကောင်များ ရှာနေသည်...</div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="bg-white p-5 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 flex-grow flex flex-col">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
                <h2 class="text-md font-bold flex items-center gap-2">🧍 လက်ရှိ ဇာတ်ကောင် (Profile)</h2>
                <button id="saveCharBtn" class="text-xs bg-indigo-600 text-white px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-indigo-700 font-medium transition-colors shadow-sm flex items-center gap-1" title="ဇာတ်ကောင်အချက်အလက်များကို သိမ်းဆည်းမည်">
                    💾 သိမ်းမည်
                </button>
            </div>
            
            <div class="space-y-4 flex-grow flex flex-col">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <div class="relative group cursor-pointer flex-shrink-0" id="avatarContainer" title="ဓာတ်ပုံထည့်မည်">
                        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-slate-100 border-2 border-indigo-100 overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm">
                            <img id="charAvatarPreview" src="" class="w-full h-full object-cover hidden">
                            <span id="charAvatarPlaceholder" class="text-2xl text-slate-400">👤</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40 rounded-full hidden group-hover:flex items-center justify-center transition-all">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="white" class="w-5 h-5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6.827 6.175A2.31 2.31 0 015.186 7.23c-.38.054-.757.112-1.134.175C2.999 7.58 2.25 8.507 2.25 9.574V18a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25h15A2.25 2.25 0 0021.75 18V9.574c0-1.067-.75-1.994-1.802-2.169a47.865 47.865 0 00-1.134-.175 2.31 2.31 0 01-1.64-1.055l-.822-1.316a2.192 2.192 0 00-1.736-1.039 48.774 48.774 0 00-5.232 0 2.192 2.192 0 00-1.736 1.039l-.821 1.316z" /><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16.5 12.75a4.5 4.5 0 11-9 0 4.5 4.5 0 019 0zM18.75 10.5h.008v.008h-.008V10.5z" /></svg>
                        </div>
                        <input type="file" id="charAvatarInput" accept="image/*" class="hidden">
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 flex-grow">
                        <label for="charName" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">အမည် (Name)</label>
                        <input id="charName" placeholder="ဥပမာ - Iron Man, GF, Boss..." class="w-full p-2.5 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all">
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 flex-grow">
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-between items-end mb-1 gap-2">
                        <label for="charDesc" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">စရိုက်လက္ခဏာ (Personality)</label>
                        <div class="flex gap-2">
                            <button id="extractLoreBtn" class="text-xs text-amber-600 hover:text-amber-800 font-bold flex items-center gap-1 transition-colors px-2 py-1 bg-amber-50 rounded-md" title="စကားပြောမှတ်တမ်းမှ အရေးကြီးအချက်အလက်များကို ဆွဲထုတ်မည်">
                                ✨ မှတ်ဉာဏ်ထုတ်မည်
                            </button>
                            <button id="genAppearanceBtn" class="text-xs text-rose-600 hover:text-rose-800 font-bold flex items-center gap-1 transition-colors px-2 py-1 bg-rose-50 rounded-md" title="ဇာတ်ကောင်၏ ပုံပန်းသဏ္ဍာန်ကို အလိုအလျောက်ဖန်တီးမည်">
                                ✨ ရုပ်ထွက်ဖန်တီးမည်
                            </button>
                            <button id="autoDescBtn" class="text-xs text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800 font-bold flex items-center gap-1 transition-colors px-2 py-1 bg-indigo-50 rounded-md">
                                ✨ အလိုအလျောက် ရေးမည်
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <textarea id="charDesc" class="w-full flex-grow min-h-[150px] p-3 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all resize-none" placeholder="ဇာတ်ကောင်၏ အပြောအဆို၊ စိတ်နေသဘောထား၊ စည်းကမ်းချက်များ..."></textarea>
                </div>

                <details class="group border border-slate-200 rounded-xl bg-slate-50 overflow-hidden">
                    <summary class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 p-3 cursor-pointer flex justify-between items-center bg-white hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
                        <span>⚙️ အထူးညွှန်ကြားချက် (Custom Instructions)</span>
                        <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
                            <svg fill="none" height="16" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
                        </span>
                    </summary>
                    <div class="p-3 border-t border-slate-200">
                        <textarea id="charInstructions" class="w-full min-h-[80px] p-2.5 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all resize-none text-sm" placeholder="ဥပမာ - ဒီစကားပြောခန်းမှာ ဇာတ်ကောင်က ကော်ဖီဆိုင်မှာ အလုပ်လုပ်နေတယ်လို့ သဘောထားပါ။ စာကို အတိုဆုံးပဲ ပြန်ပါ။"></textarea>
                    </div>
                </details>

                <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 bg-indigo-50/50 border border-indigo-100 rounded-xl">
                    <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">🎭 လက်ရှိ စိတ်ခံစားချက် (Mood):</span>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span id="moodDisplay" class="text-sm font-bold text-indigo-700">❓ မသိရသေးပါ</span>
                        <button id="checkMoodBtn" class="text-xs bg-white border border-indigo-200 text-indigo-600 px-2 py-1 rounded-md hover:bg-indigo-50 transition-colors shadow-sm">စစ်ဆေးမည်</button>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 bg-pink-50/50 border border-pink-100 rounded-xl mt-1">
                    <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">❤️ ဆက်ဆံရေး (Relationship):</span>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span id="relationshipDisplay" class="text-sm font-bold text-pink-700">❓ မသိရသေးပါ</span>
                        <button id="checkRelationshipBtn" class="text-xs bg-white border border-pink-200 text-pink-600 px-2 py-1 rounded-md hover:bg-pink-50 transition-colors shadow-sm">✨ စစ်ဆေးမည်</button>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 p-3 bg-purple-50/50 border border-purple-100 rounded-xl mt-1">
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                        <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">🧠 အတွင်းစိတ် (Inner Thoughts):</span>
                        <button id="readMindBtn" class="text-xs bg-white border border-purple-200 text-purple-600 px-2 py-1 rounded-md hover:bg-purple-50 transition-colors shadow-sm" title="ဇာတ်ကောင် လက်ရှိဘာတွေတွေးနေလဲဆိုတာကို ဖတ်ရှုမည်">✨ ဖတ်မည်</button>
                    </div>
                    <span id="mindDisplay" class="text-xs font-medium text-purple-700 italic">"..."</span>
                </div>

                <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 p-3 bg-emerald-50/50 border border-emerald-100 rounded-xl mt-1">
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                        <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">⚔️ RPG စွမ်းရည် (Stats):</span>
                        <button id="checkRpgStatsBtn" class="text-xs bg-white border border-emerald-200 text-emerald-600 px-2 py-1 rounded-md hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors shadow-sm" title="RPG ဂိမ်းကဲ့သို့ စွမ်းရည်များကို စစ်ဆေးမည်">✨ စစ်ဆေးမည်</button>
                    </div>
                    <div id="rpgStatsDisplay" class="text-xs font-medium text-emerald-700 whitespace-pre-line leading-relaxed">❓ မသိရသေးပါ</div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 hidden">
                    <input id="charImages" type="file" multiple accept="image/*" class="hidden">
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

    <div id="rightChatArea" class="w-full lg:w-2/3 flex flex-col bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden relative transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="bg-slate-50 border-b border-slate-200 px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center z-10">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <button id="toggleSidebarBtn" class="p-2 -ml-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-200 text-slate-500 transition-colors" title="Sidebar ကို အဖွင့်အပိတ်လုပ်မည်">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 6.75h16.5M3.75 12h16.5m-16.5 5.25H12" /></svg>
                </button>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <img id="chatHeaderAvatar" src="" class="w-9 h-9 rounded-full object-cover hidden border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
                    <div>
                        <h2 id="chatHeaderName" class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800">စကားပြောခန်း</h2>
                        <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500">ဓာတ်ပုံ၊ ဗီဒီယို၊ လင့်ခ်များ ပို့နိုင်ပါသည်</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <button id="summarizeChatBtn" class="text-xs text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800 font-medium px-3 py-1.5 bg-indigo-50 rounded-lg transition-colors border border-indigo-100 hidden sm:block">
                    ✨ အကျဉ်းချုပ်မည်
                </button>
                <button id="clearChatBtn" class="text-xs text-red-500 hover:text-red-700 font-medium px-3 py-1.5 bg-red-50 rounded-lg transition-colors border border-red-100">
                    🗑️ မှတ်တမ်းဖျက်မည်
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div id="chatLog" class="flex-grow p-6 overflow-y-auto flex flex-col gap-5 bg-[url('data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI0IiBoZWlnaHQ9IjQiPgo8cmVjdCB3aWR0aD0iNCIgaGVpZ2h0PSI0IiBmaWxsPSIjZmZmIi8+CjxyZWN0IHdpZHRoPSIxIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjEiIGZpbGw9IiNlNWU3ZWIiLz4KPC9zdmc+')] relative">
            </div>

        <div id="editModal" class="absolute inset-0 bg-slate-900/50 hidden items-center justify-center z-20 backdrop-blur-sm">
            <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-2xl w-11/12 max-w-lg shadow-xl flex flex-col gap-3">
                <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-800">✏️ စာပြန်ပြင်မည် (Edit Message)</h3>
                <textarea id="editMsgInput" rows="4" class="w-full p-3 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-300 rounded-xl focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 resize-none"></textarea>
                <div class="flex justify-end gap-2 mt-2">
                    <button id="cancelEditBtn" class="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 bg-slate-100 rounded-xl hover:bg-slate-200 transition-colors">ပယ်ဖျက်မည်</button>
                    <button id="saveEditBtn" class="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-white bg-indigo-600 rounded-xl hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-colors">သိမ်းမည်</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="summaryModal" class="absolute inset-0 bg-slate-900/50 hidden items-center justify-center z-30 backdrop-blur-sm">
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl w-11/12 max-w-md shadow-xl flex flex-col gap-4">
                <h3 class="text-md font-bold text-slate-800 flex items-center gap-2">✨ ဇာတ်လမ်းအကျဉ်းချုပ်</h3>
                <div id="summaryContent" class="text-sm text-slate-700 leading-relaxed max-h-60 overflow-y-auto"></div>
                <div class="flex justify-end mt-2">
                    <button id="closeSummaryBtn" class="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-white bg-indigo-600 rounded-xl hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-colors">ပိတ်မည်</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="p-4 bg-white border-t border-slate-200 relative z-10">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto flex flex-col gap-3">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
                        <button id="suggestStartersBtn" class="text-xs text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800 font-bold flex items-center gap-1 transition-colors px-3 py-1.5 bg-indigo-50 border border-indigo-100 rounded-lg">
                            ✨ စကားစရန် အကြံပြုပါ
                        </button>
                        <button id="enhanceMsgBtn" class="text-xs text-teal-600 hover:text-teal-800 font-bold flex items-center gap-1 transition-colors px-3 py-1.5 bg-teal-50 border border-teal-100 rounded-lg" title="သင်ရေးထားသောစာကို ပိုမိုကောင်းမွန်အောင် ပြင်ဆင်ပေးမည်">
                            ✨ စာသားတန်ဆာဆင်မည်
                        </button>
                        <button id="autoReplyBtn" class="text-xs text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-800 font-bold flex items-center gap-1 transition-colors px-3 py-1.5 bg-sky-50 border border-sky-100 rounded-lg" title="AI မှ သင့်ကိုယ်စား အကောင်းဆုံး စာပြန်ပေးမည်">
                            ✨ ကျွန်ုပ်ကိုယ်စား ရေးပါ
                        </button>
                        <button id="plotTwistBtn" class="text-xs text-purple-600 hover:text-purple-800 font-bold flex items-center gap-1 transition-colors px-3 py-1.5 bg-purple-50 border border-purple-100 rounded-lg hidden sm:flex" title="ဇာတ်လမ်းကို ပိုစိတ်ဝင်စားစရာကောင်းအောင် အပြောင်းအလဲတစ်ခု ဖန်တီးမည်">
                            ✨ ဇာတ်လမ်းလှည့်ကွက်
                        </button>
                        <button id="describeSceneBtn" class="text-xs text-amber-600 hover:text-amber-800 font-bold flex items-center gap-1 transition-colors px-3 py-1.5 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-100 rounded-lg hidden sm:flex" title="လက်ရှိရောက်နေသော နေရာ/မြင်ကွင်းကို ဖော်ပြပေးမည်">
                            ✨ နောက်ခံမြင်ကွင်း
                        </button>
                        <button id="narratorBtn" class="text-xs text-rose-600 hover:text-rose-800 font-bold flex items-center gap-1 transition-colors px-3 py-1.5 bg-rose-50 border border-rose-100 rounded-lg hidden sm:flex" title="18+ ကာမရာဂဆိုင်ရာ နောက်ခံမြင်ကွင်းနှင့် အဖြစ်အပျက်များကို ဖော်ပြပေးမည်">
                            🔥 18+ ဇာတ်ကြောင်းပြော
                        </button>
                        <button id="wingmanBtn" class="text-xs text-orange-600 hover:text-orange-800 font-bold flex items-center gap-1 transition-colors px-3 py-1.5 bg-orange-50 border border-orange-100 rounded-lg hidden sm:flex" title="AI ထံမှ ဘာဆက်လုပ်သင့်လဲ အကြံဉာဏ်တောင်းမည်">
                            ✨ Wingman အကြံပေး
                        </button>
                        <button id="suggestGiftBtn" class="text-xs text-pink-600 hover:text-pink-800 font-bold flex items-center gap-1 transition-colors px-3 py-1.5 bg-pink-50 border border-pink-100 rounded-lg hidden sm:flex" title="ဇာတ်ကောင်နှစ်သက်မည့် လက်ဆောင်ကို အကြံပြုပေးမည်">
